    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings across the multi-link rear suspension. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The VANOS system has been meticulously serviced to maintain variable valve timing precision. While showing minor signs of honest use consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust, offering the tactile steering feedback and high-strung performance enthusiasts demand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
