    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been well-cared for, so it's totally ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It runs smooth and looks great\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable ride without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin or have any questions at all. Can't wait to hear from you!",
