    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. To ensure structural longevity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings\u2014a critical maintenance item for this high-revving mill\u2014have been addressed. The suspension retains its telepathic feedback through refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all six cylinders remain within tight tolerances. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system refresh and valve lash adjustment, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
